2022 PH Election - Lipa City (6th District)

BBM won Lipa City with ~48%, close to his vote share in the province (~46%).

He did well in the northern areas of the city, while Leni did best in the southern area, in the brgys close to Padre Garcia and Ibaan.

#Halalan2022 https://t.co/igxa4gRc85
